data.description: Check out this charming brick ranch home that offers an idyllic retreat on 1.35 acres just minutes to Appomattox town. Step inside to discover 1,334 square feet of fantastic living space on the main level. The floor plan seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting ambiance for everyday living and entertaining. Natural light filters through the front bay windows, illuminating the interior with warmth and cheer. Three generous sized bedrooms including a spacious primary suite on the main level. An additional hall full bathroom serves the needs of family and guests with style and functionality. A 24x40 metal detached shop building beckons the hobbyist or entrepreneur, offering versatile space for projects or storage. Two detached carports provide additional covered parking options, ensuring ample space for vehicles and equipment. In the basement, a good size finished room awaits your imagination equipped with a wood stove. Amazing property!
